{"id": "art-197", "label": "Art. 197", "title": "Art. 197", "slug": "art-197", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 197 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Societatea\neste administrat&#259; de unul sau mai <span class=SpellE>mul&#355;i</span>\nadministratori, <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span> sau <span class=SpellE>neasocia&#355;i</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>numi&#355;i</span> prin actul constitutiv sau de adunarea\ngeneral&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Administratorii nu pot primi,\nf&#259;r&#259; autorizarea adun&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>,\nmandatul de administrator în alte <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>\nconcurente sau având <span class=SpellE>acela&#351;i</span> obiect de\nactivitate, nici s&#259; fac&#259; <span class=SpellE>acela&#351;i</span> fel\nde <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;</span> ori altul concurent pe cont propriu\nsau pe contul altei persoane fizice sau juridice, sub <span class=SpellE>sanc&#355;iunea</span>\nrevoc&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> r&#259;spunderii pentru daune.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)<span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nart. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>75</span><span style='color:black'>, </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>76</span><span style='color:black'>, </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>77 alin. (1)</span><span style='color:black'> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>79</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> se aplic&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> cu r&#259;spundere limitat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1485628763\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1953\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1485628763\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)<span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span> privitoare\nla administrarea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> pe <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> nu sunt aplicabile <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\ncu r&#259;spundere limitat&#259;, indiferent dac&#259; sunt sau nu supuse <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;iei</span> de auditare.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}